queries.sql: SELECT `courses`.*, acad_years.acad_year as acad_year, semesters.semester as semester_name, terms.term as term_name FROM `courses` LEFT JOIN `acad_years` ON `courses`.`acad_year_id` = `acad_years`.`id` LEFT JOIN `semesters` ON `courses`.`semester_id` = `semesters`.`id` LEFT JOIN `terms` ON `courses`.`term_id` = `terms`.`id` WHERE `courses`.`instructor_id` = '2' ORDER BY `courses`.`created_at` DESC
